>From: Richard Atwell You need to buy a tester (get the kind with two 
>gauges) and you need a supply of compressed air. Bring each cylinder to TDC 
>to do the measurement. You want to measure the percentage of leak down as 
>well as the maximum difference between any two cylinders.

